On Saturday, the Hindu Council of Kenya donated food and hygiene materials for distribution to vulnerable families around Nairobi. The event was presided over by HCK secretary Shri Surendra Bhatia. In attendance were HCK national chairman Shri Kamal Gupta and former vice chairman Shri Pravinchandra Dodhia. The donations have been made by HCK member institutions and they are meant to take place until the end of the pandemic.